theorem interior_closure_union_three_subset {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B C : Set X} :
    (interior (closure (A : Set X)) ∪ interior (closure (B : Set X)) ∪
        interior (closure (C : Set X))) ⊆
      interior (closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X)) := by
  intro x hx
  -- Break the membership in the triple union into cases.
  cases hx with
  | inl hxAB =>
      -- `x` lies in `interior (closure A) ∪ interior (closure B)`.
      cases hxAB with
      | inl hxA =>
          -- Case `x ∈ interior (closure A)`.
          have hMono : interior (closure (A : Set X)) ⊆
              interior (closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X)) := by
            have hCl : closure (A : Set X) ⊆ closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X) := by
              -- Because `A ⊆ A ∪ B ∪ C`.
              intro y hy
              exact Or.inl (Or.inl hy)
            exact interior_mono hCl
          exact hMono hxA
      | inr hxB =>
          -- Case `x ∈ interior (closure B)`.
          have hMono : interior (closure (B : Set X)) ⊆
              interior (closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X)) := by
            have hCl : closure (B : Set X) ⊆ closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X) := by
              -- Because `B ⊆ A ∪ B ∪ C`.
              intro y hy
              exact Or.inl (Or.inr hy)
            exact interior_mono hCl
          exact hMono hxB
  | inr hxC =>
      -- Case `x ∈ interior (closure C)`.
      have hMono : interior (closure (C : Set X)) ⊆
          interior (closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X)) := by
        have hCl : closure (C : Set X) ⊆ closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X) := by
          -- Because `C ⊆ A ∪ B ∪ C`.
          intro y hy
          exact Or.inr hy
        exact interior_mono hCl
      exact hMono hxC

theorem closure_subset_closure_union_three {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    {A B C : Set X} :
    closure (A : Set X) ⊆ closure (A ∪ B ∪ C : Set X) := by
  -- The set `A` is contained in `A ∪ B ∪ C`.
  have hSub : (A : Set X) ⊆ A ∪ B ∪ C := by
    intro x hx
    exact Or.inl (Or.inl hx)
  -- Taking closures preserves the inclusion.
  exact closure_mono hSub
